n而皮膚竟偷偷鬆了<br />\n為何用到盡了　至知哪樣緊要<br />\n<br />\n記住那關於光陰的教訓<br />\n回頭走天已暗<br />\n你獻出了十吋　時和分<br />\n可有換到十吋金<br />\n<br />\n還剩低　幾多心跳<br />\n人面跟水晶錶面對照<br />\n連自己　亦都分析不了　得到多與少<br />\n也許　真的瘋了<br />\n那個倒影　多麼可笑<br />\n靈魂若變賣了　上鏈也沒心跳<br />\n<br />\n銀或金　都不緊要<br />\n誰造機芯　一樣了<br />\n計劃了　照做了　得到了　時間卻太少<br />\n<br />\n還剩低　幾多心跳<br />\n還在數　趕不及了<br />\n昂貴是這刻　我覺悟了<br />\n在時計裡　看破一生　渺渺"},{"pid":"99845569e25ed5625c4ef44a4130da12f0cc0069","tid":902300,"uid":7699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c6ccbeae134515d1584df41ae163595383d276f2","tid":902300,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4d8fbf41c2b258ca328c0003f84c3b4326fedc9","tid":902300,"uid":7699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T17:09:02.000Z","msg":"做野同識朋友都係 唔好擺太多感情落去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T17:10:47.000Z","msg":"有時係咪做人其實短視啲仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n特別係友誼方面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T17:39:21.000Z","msg":"朋友用黎出賣 呢句說話以前聽好un耳 依家先覺得係啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31bc99c59975e5c11c86a30c6116dbc4f66aca9f","tid":902300,"uid":217460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T17:42:40.000Z","msg":"錢唔係萬能<br />\n但冇錢就萬萬不能<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2a153636017575885b955c51d071563f6174e2","tid":902300,"uid":63842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"99845569e25ed5625c4ef44a4130da12f0cc0069","tid":902300,"uid":7699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c6ccbeae134515d1584df41ae163595383d276f2","tid":902300,"uid":63842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4d8fbf41c2b258ca328c0003f84c3b4326fedc9","tid":902300,"uid":7699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T17:09:02.000Z","msg":"做野同識朋友都係 唔好擺太多感情落去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T17:10:47.000Z","msg":"有時係咪做人其實短視啲仲好